Care Requests
POST /patient_api/care_requests → create
GET /patient_api/care_requests → index
GET /patient_api/care_requests/:id → show
POST /patient_api/care_requests/:care_request_id/mark_read → mark_read
POST /patient_api/care_requests/:care_request_id/stacks → create (for stacks)

Question Sets
PATCH /patient_api/question_sets/:id → update

Attachments
GET /patient_api/attachments/:id → show

Referrals
POST /patient_api/referrals/:referral_id/messages → create (for referral messages)
GET /patient_api/referrals/:referral_id/messages → index (for referral messages)

Referral Messages
POST /patient_api/referral_messages/:referral_message_id/mark_read → mark_read